Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总共1500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再卖那么廉价的扇子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须多卖些贵的棋盘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这不是御器曾老师吗？
