Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:26.90,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fad(488,560)\3c&HCB0000&\bord2\pos(509,296)}优希
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:26.90,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1C79E0&\bord2\fs20\fad(488,560)\pos(112,288)}由香里老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:26.34,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来试试吧
